                    data-src="https://web.devpgs.com/lawsuaecab-2023/ar/materials/22295/previous?modificationsUrl=https%3A%2F%2Fweb.devpgs.com%2Flawsuaecab-2023%2Far%2Flegislations%2F1426%2Fmodifications">
                    <i class="icon icon-alert-icon yellow_"></i><span>
                      النصوص السابقة</span>
